# Re-Entrancy Attacks

## Def (when this happens mostly):

```Solidity
   When the state is not been updated before the external call.
```

### Types :

* Classic Reentrancy
* Cross-Function Reentrancy
* Cross- Contract Reentrancy
* Read-only Reentrancy

### Tips to find it out.

1. Pay Close attention to every external call.
2. Collect all the external calls which are occured before updating the state (slither can help in this alot)
3.

